				<h1>2013 Forecast: Malware, scams, security and privacy concerns</h1>
<div class="excerpt">What does the New Year hold for information security, malicious software, consumer privacy and cybercrime? Questions of this mature are posed by journalists toward the end of every year and, beginning about November, answers from security specialists start to appear in print. Indeed, ESET researchers in Latin America published a 20-page white paper on this</div>
